com.stefanie20.ReadDay

类 Readability

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stefanie20.ReadDay.Readability

  • public class Readability
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to get information about Readability view. A Readability object also represent a object containing Readability web content.
